---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<Layout title="AETHER | Protocolo de Inicio">

	<main class="relative z-10 w-full min-h-screen bg-black flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-6 select-none overflow-hidden">

		<div class="absolute inset-0 dot-grid-bg pointer-events-none opacity-50"></div>

		<div class="max-w-4xl w-full space-y-24 text-center relative z-20">

			<header class="space-y-6 animate-in fade-in duration-1000 slide-in-from-bottom-10">
				<h1 class="text-7xl md:text-8xl font-light tracking-tight text-white font-mono drop-shadow-lg opacity-90">
					AETHER
				</h1>
				<p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-cyan-400 font-mono tracking-widest uppercase max-w-xl mx-auto">
					Protocolo de Inicio
				</p>
				<p class="text-sm md:text-lg text-zinc-400 font-light max-w-2xl mx-auto italic">
					Transmite tu pensamiento al vacío. Donde cada señal es un eco fugaz en el universo digital.
				</p>
			</header>

			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 text-left animate-in fade-in duration-1000 delay-300 slide-in-from-bottom-10 fill-mode-backwards">

				<div class="space-y-3 p-5 border border-zinc-900/80 bg-zinc-950/40 rounded-lg hover:border-cyan-800 transition-all duration-300 group shadow-xl">
					<div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-md flex items-center justify-center text-cyan-400 mb-2 transition-colors">
						<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M2 12s3-7 10-7 10 7 10 7-3 7-10 7-10-7-10-7Z"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/></svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-white font-mono uppercase tracking-wider text-xs">Libertad sin Juicios</h3>
					<p class="text-zinc-500 text-xs leading-relaxed">
						Expresa lo que sientes sin miedo. Aquí no hay perfiles ni historial, solo tu mensaje puro y anónimo.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="space-y-3 p-5 border border-zinc-900/80 bg-zinc-950/40 rounded-lg hover:border-cyan-800 transition-all duration-300 group shadow-xl">
					<div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-md flex items-center justify-center text-cyan-400 mb-2 transition-colors">
						<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2v4"/><path d="m16.2 7.8 2.9-2.9"/><path d="M18 12h4"/><path d="m16.2 16.2 2.9 2.9"/><path d="M12 18v4"/><path d="m4.9 19.1 2.9-2.9"/><path d="M2 12h4"/><path d="m4.9 4.9 2.9 2.9"/></svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-white font-mono uppercase tracking-wider text-xs">Desahogo Fugaz</h3>
					<p class="text-zinc-500 text-xs leading-relaxed">
						Libera esa carga mental. Tus palabras se desvanecen en el tiempo, perfecto para soltar y seguir adelante.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="space-y-3 p-5 border border-zinc-900/80 bg-zinc-950/40 rounded-lg hover:border-cyan-800 transition-all duration-300 group shadow-xl">
					<div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-md flex items-center justify-center text-cyan-400 mb-2 transition-colors">
						<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 2a14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0 20 14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0-20"/><path d="M2 12h20"/></svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-white font-mono uppercase tracking-wider text-xs">Sintonía Global</h3>
					<p class="text-zinc-500 text-xs leading-relaxed">
						Sintoniza con otros humanos. Lee lo que el mundo está sintiendo o pensando en este preciso instante.
					</p>
				</div>

			</div>

			<div class="animate-in fade-in duration-1000 delay-500 slide-in-from-bottom-10 fill-mode-backwards">
				<a
					href="/app"
					class="group relative inline-flex items-center gap-4 px-8 py-3 bg-cyan-600/10 border border-cyan-500/30 text-cyan-300 font-mono text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] hover:bg-cyan-600/20 transition-all duration-200 shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(6,182,212,0.5)] hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(6,182,212,0.8)]"
				>
					Iniciar Secuencia
					<svg class="w-4 h-4 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1 text-cyan-400" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
				</a>
			</div>

		</div>
	</main>
</Layout>